  <h2>Tech Stack</h2>

  <ul>
    <li><strong>Server:</strong> Node.js + Fastify</li>
    <li><strong>UI:</strong> Astro SSR + React islands + Tailwind CSS</li>
    <li><strong>Database:</strong> PostgreSQL (data) + Redis (cache)</li>
    <li><strong>Build:</strong> pnpm + Turborepo</li>
    <li><strong>SDKs:</strong> TypeScript (polling), Kotlin (coroutines)</li>
  </ul>

